The paper deals with adaptive link selection strategies for distributed estimation in wireless sensor networks, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and mathematical analysis (cs.MA). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
